itunes:summary:
Tamica AKA The Orgasmic Mama is a Melbourne-baseed somatic sex coach and multi-qualified therapist with a deep passion for teaching humans to re-attune to the wisdom of our bodies, while giving full permission to shamelessly prioritise pleasure and play. She believes that our cultural narratives around sex, intimacy, pleasure and relationships need a damn good shake up! Never one to shy away from a challenge, Tamica is committed to leading the charge. 

Book: Wild Honey by Debut Books
Instagram: @theorgasmicmama
Website: https://www.theorgasmicmama.com/
